ons-avec-george-r-r-martin-et-john-howe-30-11-2018-2275521_2957.php \"D\u00e9couvrez le 1er \u00e9pisode de Dragons, avec George R. R. Martin et John Howe\"]. ''[[Le Point]]''. November 30, 2018.</ref>\n|}\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist|refs=\n<ref name=\"middlename\">{{cite web|last=Richards |first=Linda |url=http://januarymagazine.com/profiles/grrmartin.html |title=January interview: George R.R. Martin |publisher=[[January Magazine|januarymagazine.com]] |date=January 2001 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120320033411/http://januarymagazine.com/profiles/grrmartin.html |archivedate=March 20, 2012 |url-status=live |access-date=January 21, 2012 }}</ref>\n<ref name=\"confirmation\">{{cite news |url=http://tamutimes.tamu.edu/2013/03/22/author-george-r-r-martin-is-visiting-texas-am-talks-game-of-thrones-and-texas-am-libraries/ |title=Author George R.R. Martin Is Visiting Texas A&M, Talks 'Game of Thrones' and Texas A&M Libraries |publisher=Texas A&M University |work=TAMUTimes |date=March 22, 2013 |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20130326010252/http://tamutimes.tamu.edu/2013/03/22/author-george-r-r-martin-is-visiting-texas-am-talks-game-of-thrones-and-texas-am-libraries |archivedate=March 26, 2013}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"grrm\">{{cite news|url=http://www.timesrecordnews.com/news/2011/sep/22/quest-into-world-of-fantasy-books-can-be-hobbit//|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130409090228/http://www.timesrecordnews.com/news/2011/sep/22/quest-into-world-of-fantasy-books-can-be-hobbit//|url-status=dead|archive-date=April 9, 2013|title=Choate: Quest into world of fantasy books can be hobbit-forming|last=Choate|first=Trish|date=September 22, 2011|work=[[Times Record News]]|access-date=February 28, 2012}}</ref>\n}}\n\n==External links==\n{{Library resources box}}\n{{Sister project links|d=Q181677|c=category:George R. R. Martin|n=no|b=no|v=no|voy=no|m=no|mw=no|s=no|wikt=no|species=no}}\n* {{official website|www.georgerrmartin.com}}\n* {{LiveJournal|grrm|George 